{"word":"G5563 - χωρίζω - chōrízō - kho-rid'-zo - Depart","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χωρίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chōrízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kho-rid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Depart</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிரி, விட்டுப்போ, விட்டுப்பிரி விலகு"},{"paragraph":"1. to separate, divide, part, put asunder"},{"paragraph":"2. to leave a husband or wife: of divorce"},{"paragraph":"3. to depart, go away"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5561 - χώρα - chṓra - kho'-rah/5561\">G5561</a>; <i>to place room</i> between, that is, <i>part</i>; reflexively to <i>go away:</i> - depart, put asunder, separate.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}